data.description: Welcome to Cornerstone! This newly constructed property feature 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms located in Fairburn is a must-see. It is spacious open concept floorplan with updated fixtures and appliances. The kitchen has granite countertops, an island mini bar, oversized walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliance's with the REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED!, 42" Cabinets and an eat in kitchen. Crown molding is through the main level of the home with an electric fire place in the living room. Backyard is cleared, leveled and fenced in. The primary bedroom has double vanities, separate tub and shower, and large walk-in closets and plenty of space to have a sitting area. All the secondary room have large closets for additional storage. Both indoor and outdoor entertaining can be achieved with plenty of parking. Enjoy a No HOA, very well maintained community. Conveniently located near dining, shopping, entertainment, and an easy commute to downtown and the airport. Don't hesitate. Schedule your private tour today.  For virtual showing please use the link: https://www.rockhavenga.com/plans/abbot/
